data.description:
3 BR ranch, Landscaped, Master Bath and walk-in closet.  

Neighborhood Description

Very quite and lots of kids.  The new Evans Skate Park is just around the corner and it has a soccer field and Basketball Court.  Large Playground Equipment for the little kids.  View up the street is marvelous during the holidays.
data.whatILove: Great Room encapsilates Kitchen, dining and living rooms.  Spacious without being too big.  1 nearly finished Office/Entertainment room in basement (its currently my weight room) and 1 Framed out, drywalled and carpeted room in basement.  Rough in for possible basement bath between the two rooms.  Laundry room framed in.  Low heating bills and water bills.  One of the few homes in the area that has central air.  Lots of storage and closet space.  South side of house is a Dog run with Digging area.
